headline: RITZ Crackers Introduces Swicy New Flavor: Hot Honey
summary: The RITZ Brand is excited to announce the launch of its newest flavor innovation: Hot Honey. This new flavor is sure to excite taste buds everywhere and stand out among the increasingly popular swicy (sweet + spicy) snack offerings.

headline: Shelton Equity Income Strategy Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: During the fourth quarter, the Equity Income Portfolio underperformed the CBOE BuyWrite Index by 5.50%, delivering a gross return of 0.28% (-0.05% net) compared to the BXM return of 5.78%.
